headline: AWAKE Caffeinated Chocolate Makes Delicious Debut in U.S. Costco Warehouses
summary: AWAKE Chocolate, the maker of delicious and functional caffeinated chocolate bites and bars, today announced its exciting entry into Costco warehouses throughout the Southeast United States. Beginning August 8 and running through October 31, Costco members will be able to purchase the exclusive 32-count Dark Chocolate Variety Pack, featuring fan-favorite Dark Chocolate Salted Caramel and Dark Chocolate Salted Almond bites.
